<SECOND>AM-Convenience Stripper,0353</SECOND>
<HEAD>Man Arrested After Stripping in Store's Candy Aisle</HEAD>
<DATELINE>ABILENE, Texas (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
 A convenience store clerk was treated to a little adult entertainment when a man stripped down to a G-string and leather jacket and bumped and ground his way down the candy aisle. Circle K clerk <PERSON> Annette </PERSON> <PERSON> Ochoa </PERSON> said a man entered the store about 3 a.m. Friday and asked if he could use the restroom. She told him this was n't permitted to customers, and the man smiled and left. But minutes later he returned while she was talking on the phone. `` When I looked up, he was standing there with nothing but a G-string and leather jacket on,'' <PERSON> Ochoa </PERSON> said. `` I told my friend, ` I've got a stripper, I'll have to call the cops.''' Once the stripper had her attention, he began performing. `` He walked up, picked up a <ORGANIZATION> Thrifty </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Nickel </ORGANIZATION> -LRB- newspaper -RRB- and did some pumping motions, if you know what I mean,'' <PERSON> Ochoa </PERSON> said. `` Then he went down one aisle and then came up the candy aisle and stood in front of the candy counter and did some more of his motions. He heard me say I was calling the police, but he just stood there until I dialed the numbers. Then he left.'' The stripper did n't know when to quit his act though. He was arrested on a complaint of indecent exposure shortly after he appeared outside another convenience store. He was released without any charge being filed, but police are still investigating. `` I was talking to my friend -LRB- at a second store -RRB- when she spotted the guy walking around outside her store,'' <PERSON> Ochoa </PERSON> said. `` About that time a cop walked in to ask me some follow-up questions and I told him what was going on. He radioed it in and a cop who was nearby caught him near the store on Lakeshore Drive. He was only wearing his G-string and a leather jacket.'' <PERSON> Ochoa </PERSON> says the strip show was something of a shock. Still, she believes something good came from his performance. `` It kept me awake.''
